N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 331.11 - Meetings

State Regulations

The senate shall meet at least twice a year at such times
and places as shall be determined by the executive committee. Special meetings
of the senate may be called in accordance with the provisions of the
bylaws. Notes
